<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <title>MyR</title>
</head>
<header>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-white display-2">MyR</h1>
        <h2 class="text-white my-4">GAMES I'VE PLAYED</h2>
    </div>
</header>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="text-white fs-4">An overall <b>review/experince</b> about the games that I played. All the games can be identified using steam via appid or the name of the game. This page will be updated frequently based on how frequently I play, So might as well bookmark it if wanna check on me ;)</p>
        <p class="text-white fs-4">Sort by <a href="#">G.O.A.T</a>, <a href="#">Latest</a> or by <a href="#">Title</a>.</p>
        <p class="text-white fs-4">If you want to check out my portfolio or my projects feel free to visit my <a href="">website</a>. Lets connect there!</p>
        <p class="border-bottom mt-1"></p>
        <% games.forEach(game => { %>
        <div class="card flex-row my-5 cards">
            <img class="card-img-sm-left" src="<%= game.imageurl %>"/>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title h2 h2-sm text-white"><%= game.name %></h4>
              <p class="card-text text-color"><b>Developer: </b><%= game.developer %> | <b>Played at: </b><%= game.playedat %></p>
              <p class="card-text text-color"><b>How strongly I recommend playing: </b><%= game.rating %>/10</p>
              <p class="card-text text-white"></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% }) %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>